# PROTOTYPE-01: Core Ingestion, Normalization, and Real-Time View

**Status**: Prototype Definition

This document outlines the minimal viable architecture for the core log collection pipeline. It features an authentication mechanism, a high-speed HTTP endpoint for plain-text log ingestion, scalable string-manipulation normalization workers, and a role-based real-time web view for engineers and administrators.

*Note: Durable storage, asynchronous AI classification, and alerting (e.g., Telegram notifications) are explicitly excluded from this phase.*

